# {{projectName}}

A production-ready **{{#if (eq framework "selenium")}}Selenium WebDriver{{else}}Playwright{{/if}}** test automation
framework using **{{#if (eq testRunner "testng")}}TestNG{{else}}JUnit5{{/if}}** and **{{#if (eq buildTool
"maven")}}Maven{{else}}Gradle{{/if}}**.

## 🚀 Quick Start

```bash
# Run all tests
{{#if (eq buildTool "maven")}}
mvn clean test
{{else}}
gradle clean test
{{/if}}

# Run with specific browser
{{#if (eq buildTool "maven")}}
mvn test -Dbrowser=firefox
{{else}}
gradle test -Dbrowser=firefox
{{/if}}

# Run headless
{{#if (eq buildTool "maven")}}
mvn test -Dheadless=true
{{else}}
gradle test -Dheadless=true
{{/if}}

# Run specific environment
{{#if (eq buildTool "maven")}}
mvn test -Denv=qa
{{else}}
gradle test -Denv=qa
{{/if}}
```

