## Running on Sauce Labs

Sauce Labs integration requires wiring a `RemoteWebDriver` in
`core/BrowserFactory.java`. The canonical form:

```java
Capabilities caps = new DesiredCapabilities();
caps.setCapability("browserName", "chrome");
caps.setCapability("platformName", "Windows 11");
URL hub = new URL(
    "https://" + System.getenv("SAUCE_USERNAME") + ":" + System.getenv("SAUCE_ACCESS_KEY")
        + "@ondemand.saucelabs.com/wd/hub"
);
return new RemoteWebDriver(hub, caps);
```

Then set `SAUCE_USERNAME` + `SAUCE_ACCESS_KEY` env vars and run `mvn test`.
Sessions appear at https://app.saucelabs.com/dashboard.

